go for dinner.  sit next to the wood-burning oven. the food is locally grown and market-sourced.  farm-to-table yumminess. PRO:     - wilted spinach pizza     - deviled eggs with salmon roe     - seasonal fried artichokes     - creative drinks:  nutty cider & gin(ny) STAFF:     - incredibly warm hospitality (thanks for a lovely evening, Jesse & James)
